WEBVTT

00:00:00.000 --> 00:00:20.000
Welcome to British English Academy A1-M01: Identity, goals and learner profile. Learners practise give personal information through introductions, routines, aspirations, personal information. The teacher models be / have got, introduces vocabulary such as personal details, goals, classroom objects, numbers, dates, then learners complete quiz, evidence upload and reflection.
